Changes in PopGenome 2.0.5
===========================

BUG FIXED:
- include.unknown was bugy when the very first individual was unknown.

NEW FEATURES:
- splitting.data(..., whole.data=FALSE)
  works now for multiple regions when the 
  regions cannot be concatenated.


