Changes in PopGenome 2.0
==========================

BUGS FIXED:

- U,u was not accepted as a nucleotide (readData)

NEW FEATURES:

- PopGenome no longer depends on the ape package
- Whop_readVCF (an interface to the WhopGenome package)


Changes in PopGenome 1.3.0
==========================

